Paper: hep-th/0205308

Date: 2002-05-30

Title: WDVV Equations as Functional Relations

Authors: H.W. Braden and A. Marshakov

Comments: 9 pages LaTex

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B541 (2002) 376-383

We discuss the associativity or WDVV equations and demonstrate that they canbe rewritten as certain functional relations between the {\it second}derivatives of a single function, similar to the dispersionless Hirotaequations. The properties of these functional relations are further discussed.